<title>USA: Today's Man names Johnson exec vp/CFO.</title>
<headline>Today's Man names Johnson exec vp/CFO.</headline>
<dateline>MOORESTOWN, N.J. 1997-04-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Today's Man Inc said Tuesday it promoted Frank Johnson to executive vice president, chief financial officer and treasurer from vice president, chief financial officer and treasurer.</p>
<p>The company said it promoted Johnson and three other executives as part of its plan to reorganize and ultimately to emerge from Chapter 11.</p>
